          </tbody>
          <caption>Source: PW OnlyIAS Mains analysis (2018-2024).</caption>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="pyq-insight"><strong>GS2:</strong> Polity is king — always 9-10 Qs (half the paper). IR stable at 3-4 Qs. Governance increasingly uses case-study format.</div>

