        <div class="pq-tip"><span class="pq-tip__icon">1️⃣</span><div><p class="pq-tip__title">Topic-wise, not year-wise</p><p class="pq-tip__desc">Group by topic (all Polity PYQs together). Reveals which sub-topics UPSC returns to.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pq-tip"><span class="pq-tip__icon">2️⃣</span><div><p class="pq-tip__title">Attempt before reading notes</p><p class="pq-tip__desc">Can't answer? Now you know what to focus on. Can? Move faster through that topic.</p></div></div>
