        <div class="pq-tip"><span class="pq-tip__icon">4️⃣</span><div><p class="pq-tip__title">Track frequency</p><p class="pq-tip__desc">5+ times in 10 years = UPSC favourite. Invest disproportionate time there.</p></div></div>
