        <div class="pq-tip"><span class="pq-tip__icon">6️⃣</span><div><p class="pq-tip__title">Revise with PYQs as flashcards</p><p class="pq-tip__desc">Can you answer each confidently? If not, revisit. PYQs = ultimate revision checklist.</p></div></div>
